message.raw:
Implemented support for PyQt as well as PySide.
GUI toolkit to PyQt unless PySide has already been imported.

* License updated to support free and commercial versions of PyQt
* Generalised the UiLoader class to provide a common interface for loading ui files for both PyQt and PySide
